+apps/web/lib/shared/wall-clock-time.ts             | 142 +++++++++++++
+10 files changed, 765 insertions(+), 39 deletions(-)
+```
+
+VERDICT: fail
+
+1. Remove the ambiguous product-ID fallback in dependency linking; missing/unmatched BOM-line identity must produce an explicit failure (or a proven unique legacy mapping), and add the negative duplicate-product test.
+2. Fix wall-clock candidate validation to compare all requested date/time parts, define and test the exact spring-gap policy, and test the standard-time choice for a fall-back ambiguity.
+3. Store and compare per-day usage as integer milliseconds end-to-end; add a repeated small-duration test proving the 361st one-minute WO is rejected from a 6-hour bucket.

